    <p>• Brook­lyn Nets star Kyrie Irv­ing said he wants the money the Na­tional Bas­ket­ball As­so­ci­a­tion (NBA) fined him for his re­fusal to speak to the me­dia to help “marginalis­ed com­mu­ni­ties” and im­plied he does not plan to talk to re­porters any time soon.</p>
    <p>The NBA fined the 28-year-old and the Nets US$25,000 (S$33,430) each on Thurs­day for vi­o­lat­ing the league’s me­dia rules.</p>


